{"tid":1537333,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[求求大家幫手］對抗香港電台白色恐怖 支持Rthk 姐姐/港台嬸嬸","createTime":"2019-09-04T01:40:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T15:44:05.000Z","uid":38677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fc02657320c66cc10f93d9e3c04854b9fcb2eaf9","tid":1537333,"uid":38677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:40:45.000Z","msg":"港台記者陳妙玲追問警察，但被撐警組織發動投訴攻勢，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">企圖製造白色恐怖，逼令港台炒佢魷魚！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n希望各位幫幫忙，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">發起一人一信支持陳妙玲！支持良心記者！<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n感激不盡<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n收信地址：ccu@rthk.hk<br />\n<br />\n香港電台 廣播處長大鑒<br />\n<br />\n本人為香港電台的長期聽眾，十分感謝港台新聞部，特別是陳妙玲小姐的報道。她在不同場合中展示了記者的天職，把握機會對政府在各項市民關心的議題上努力追問尋求真相，以理性及中立態度偵查問題根源，藉報道揭示香港種種問題。<br />\n<br />\n謹請香港電台代本人向記者陳妙玲轉達由衷感激。本人深信香港電台會一如既往，保持中立，以事實報道真相，肩負香港人聲音的廣播重任。<br />\n<br />\n2019年9月初"},{"pid":"8efb527611e6cc430af8c91fcb197f80d586c92d","tid":1537333,"uid":52727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:41:11.000Z","msg":"【教學】將Facebook/Youtube 影片文宣轉換成Twitter 文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1537277\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1537277</a><br />\n<br />\n1. 註冊Twitter 帳號。<br />\n2. 找到要post 上Twitter 的影片。<br />\n3. 複制facebook影片連結貼上到以下網頁 (需要登入及縛定Twitter 帳戶， facebook影片分享必需是公開)。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://transferring-videos.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftransferring-videos.com&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3B%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=1a8ac711\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://transferring-videos.com</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 等待轉換時輸入英文標題，及加上 #chinazi 等 hash tag。<br />\n5. 選擇發佈至 Twitter。<br />\n<br />\n6. 【重要】我諗大家嘅Twitter應該都冇乜人follow, 記得copy自己Twitter post 嘅link, 然後貼上到名人的Twitter post 上！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我做咗幾日已經多咗好多外國人睇，甚至開始有支那打手過黎留言。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"594fc30396cfec75a2a93ae19a1581377ac3c306","tid":1537333,"uid":38677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:41:14.000Z","msg":"請大家幫手推推"},{"pid":"484bea9f9c18e96ffe636a5b44437f414a56e381","tid":1537333,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:41:53.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be66114b2cd72224f880d3a5ed1603d659a12c3a","tid":1537333,"uid":134107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:42:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B8W7Cuk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%